  - elementId: formula-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 355, 1120, 60]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>Score = (Skills x 0.40) + (Experience x 0.30) + (Education x 0.15) + (Projects x 0.15)</p>
  - elementId: pipeline-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 445, 300, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>AI PIPELINE</strong></p>
  - elementId: pipeline
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 480, 1160, 130]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      lineHeight: 1.7
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p><span style="color:$accent;"><strong>1. Parse</strong></span>  PDF resume → text extraction (pdf-parse)   <span style="color:$accent;"><strong>2. Extract</strong></span>  Skills, experience, education (Gemini API)   <span style="color:$accent;"><strong>3. Match</strong></span>  Semantic comparison with job requirements</p>
        <p><span style="color:$accent;"><strong>4. Score</strong></span>  Weighted algorithm across 4 dimensions   <span style="color:$accent;"><strong>5. Rank</strong></span>  Sort candidates by overall score   <span style="color:$accent;"><strong>6. Summarize</strong></span>  AI-generated summary + skill gaps</p>